room_title: Escape room "Mission: Homeland" by Riddle in Mashpee
room_description:
You are an employee of the D.O.D., working for PAVE PAWS to protect the eastern seaboard from foreign threats and incoming missiles. You have long suspected one of your co-workers to be a double agent, working for Russia.
You break into his office only to discover the truth: he IS a double agent and he has jammed the radar system giving the Russians a clear path to launch their nuclear missiles at the United States. You have 60 minutes to re-activate the warning system, launch the counterattack and save your homeland from becoming a nuclear wasteland. Are you Americaâ€™s next hero?
